    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="header-content">
                <div class="logo">
                    <i class="fas fa-shipping-fast"></i>
                </div>
                <h1>美育未来物流查询系统</h1>
                <p>输入手机号即可查询您的物流状态</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="search-section" id="searchSection">
            <div class="input-group">
                <label for="phoneInput"><i class="fas fa-mobile-alt"></i> 请输入手机号：</label>
                <i class="fas fa-phone"></i>
                <input 
                    type="text" 
                    id="phoneInput" 
                    placeholder="请输入11位手机号码" 
                    maxlength="11"
                    oninput="this.value = this.value.replace(/\D/g, '')"
                >
            </div>
            
            <button class="btn" onclick="searchLogistics()">
                <i class="fas fa-search"></i> 立即查询
            </button>
            
            <div class="error-message" id="errorMessage">
                <i class="fas fa-exclamation-circle"></i> 未找到该手机号对应的物流信息，请核对后重试。
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="result-section" id="resultSection">
            <div class="result-card">
                <div class="result-item">
                    <span class="result-label"><i class="fas fa-mobile-alt"></i> 手机号：</span>
                    <span class="result-value" id="resultPhone">13800138000</span>
                </div>
                <div class="result-item">
                    <span class="result-label"><i class="fas fa-barcode"></i> 物流单号：</span>
                    <span class="result-value" id="resultNu">YT7579138178139</span>
                </div>
                <div class="result-item">
                    <span class="result-label"><i class="fas fa-shipping-fast"></i> 快递公司：</span>
                    <span class="result-value" id="resultCom">圆通速递</span>
                </div>
                <div class="result-item">
                    <span class="result-label"><i class="fas fa-store"></i> 发货状态：</span>
                    <span class="result-value" id="resultStatus">运输中</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="action-buttons">
                <button class="action-btn query-btn" onclick="openKuaidi100()">
                    <i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i> 查看详细物流
                </button>
                <button class="action-btn back-btn" onclick="backToSearch()">
                    <i class="fas fa-arrow-left"></i> 返回查询
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p><i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i> 温馨提示：查询结果来自快递100，信息仅供参考</p>
            <p>© 2024 美育未来物流查询系统</p>
